 * 26.10.2012 (1.2.0.10)
    - updated for minecraft 1.4.2
    - added bats (witches and wither skeletons don't work yet)

 * 27.08.2012 (1.1.1.9)
    - fixed slime chunks

 * 21.08.2012 (1.1.1.8)
    - added a selection GUI with all vanilla monsters that can spawn naturally
    - changed the highlighting (night only check for monsters, day only check for animals, no check for other monsters)

 * 16.08.2012 (1.1.0.7)
    - updated for minecraft 1.3.2

 * 14.08.2012 (1.1.0.6)
    - updated for minecraft 1.3.1
    - moved the configuration to Forge's config system

 * 25.06.2012 (1.0.1.4)
    - Forge compatible version
    - added guides

 * 22.06.2012 (1.0.1.3)
    - the renderer creates a ghost cave spider and ghost zombie entity as a reference for spawn checks

 * 20.06.2012 (1.0.0.2)
    - non-opaque solid blocks (class, fences, leaves etc) now work correctly

 * 18.06.2012 (1.0.0.1)
